{"tid":1757341,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"《全民勇武》無行動，唔代表無野做，全部人即刻去練體能","createTime":"2019-11-26T12:55:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T15:16:44.000Z","uid":293677,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"83fd3ac7c737167caedc030fff67aa7ffc993f87","tid":1757341,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T12:55:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />是咁的<br />\n古語有云：修身齊家治國平天下<br />\n要做大事，就要先裝備好自己<br />\n只係想提醒手足呢場係長期戰爭<br />\n呢場革命運動未完架<br />\n平日要抽時間出黎<br />\n每個香港人都應該要提升自己既體能<br />\n<br />\n大方向就係：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全民運動，全民健身，<br />\n然後全民習武，<br />\n最後達至&quot;全民勇武&quot;</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你唔打得 都起要跑得<br />\n滅少補擒獲既機會<br />\n香港人唔洗服兵役<br />\n長期以來又賤視體育運動科目<br />\n搞到個個體能好差<br />\n上到戰場<br />\n淨係個心勇係唔夠架<br />\n人數再多都係散兵游勇<br />\n<br />\n引用普京一句說話：<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有實力的憤怒是毫無意義的</span></span></strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n利申：自知體能太弱，上到戰場只係做炮灰<br />\n小弟從六月已經開始舉鐵，之後買埋奶粉飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n共勉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人，運動<br />\n香港人，健身<br />\n香港人，習武"},{"pid":"757b1fad60e1119bd073b3466a0075ebdfeb1dac","tid":1757341,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T12:56:57.000Z","msg":"好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b4faa0c7738b669233f351dff0da1ce0d533e8e","tid":1757341,"uid":242278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T12:57:18.000Z","msg":"岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56cce3d660fc0ef67c89a6c7c5707244fb213c5b","tid":1757341,"uid":10274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T12:58:30.000Z","msg":"怕香港人善忘嘅，推行動post 啦